(3, 6, 'Part 2', '{\"bn\": \"<div class=\\\"container my-3\\\">\\r\\n            <h2 class=\\\"font-weight-normal text-8 text-center\\\">কিভাবে লগইন করবেন?</h2>\\r\\n            <div class=\\\"row pb-2 mt-4\\\">\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"col-12\\\">\\r\\n                    <h4>১. লগইন বাটনে  ক্লিক করুন। </h4>\\r\\n                    <img class=\\\"img-fluid border-radius-0\\\" src=\\\"https://www.marriagematchbd.com/storage/media_images/YYwP23090625.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                </div>\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"col-12 mt-4\\\">\\r\\n                    <h4>২. আপনার ইমেইল ও পাসওয়ার্ড দিয়ে লগইন করুন। </h4>\\r\\n                    <img class=\\\"img-fluid border-radius-0\\\" src=\\\"https://www.marriagematchbd.com/storage/media_images/Wh4T23090732.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                </div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-12 mt-4\\\">\\r\\n                    <h4>৩. আমার ড্যাশবোর্ডে গিয়ে প্রয়োজনীয় তথ্য আপডেট করুন। </h4>\\r\\n                    <img class=\\\"img-fluid border-radius-0\\\" src=\\\"https://www.marriagematchbd.com/storage/media_images/VyJg23090606.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                </div>\\r\\n            </div>\\r\\n        </div>\", \"en\": \"<div class=\\\"container my-3\\\">\\r\\n            <h2 class=\\\"font-weight-normal text-8 text-center\\\">How to login?</h2>\\r\\n            <div class=\\\"row pb-2 mt-4\\\">\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"col-12\\\">\\r\\n                    <h4>1. Click on login button.</h4>\\r\\n                    <img class=\\\"img-fluid border-radius-0\\\" src=\\\"https://www.marriagematchbd.com/storage/media_images/YYwP23090625.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n                </div>\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"col-12 mt-4\\\">\\r\\n                    <h4>2. Login with your email and password. </h4>\\r\\n                    <img class=\\\"img-fluid border-radius-0\\\" src=\\\"https://www.marriagematchbd.com/storage/media_images/Wh4T23090732.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\">\\r\\n      